## ✏️ Initialization Methods

### 1️⃣ Array Initializer
```java
int[] no = {1, 2, 3, 4, 5};
```

### 2️⃣ Individual Assignment
```java
int[] no = new int[8];
no[0] = 10;
no[1] = 20;
```

### 3️⃣ Runtime Initialization
```java
int[] no = new int[5];
for (int i = 0; i < no.length; i++) {
    no[i] = i + 1;
}
```

